transArray.content: The room facilities are very good, relatively smart, and quite quiet. There is a washing machine downstairs, and the food delivery is done by robots, which is very convenient. What needs to be improved is to protect the privacy of guests. When I finished entering my personal information, the user next to me Come and take a look too

Dear guests, you look up at the fireworks, but there is a brighter light in your eyes than the fireworks. The light of fireworks is only a moment. The light in your eyes is eternal. I love you, little man.
